rows.name:
Foorara contacted home guild to
report Walky-Walky finished, and
they sent Nopon to bring home!

rows.label: qst500209_msg0002
rows.name:
Thought of going back to days of
elite schooling at Voltis Trade Guild
not make Foorara very happy...

rows.label: qst500209_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh yes, did Foorara not mention?
Foorara is heir of Voltis Trade Guild.

rows.label: qst500209_msg0004
rows.name:
Training very hard every day to
make Voltis best Nopon Trade Guild
and beat Avaritia.

rows.label: qst500209_msg0005
rows.name:
But thanks to all memories of meeting
friends on travels, Foorara be able to
survive tough education now.

rows.label: qst500209_msg0006
rows.name:
Here, this is thanks for friends
from Foorara!

rows.label: qst500209_msg0007
rows.name:
It Foorara who should be
thanking friends!

rows.label: qst500209_msg0008
rows.name:
Foorara hope friends stay well and
keep working for sake of Alst!
